<http://www.example.org/medicalOntology#FSCA-001> <http://www.example.org/medicalOntology#status> "Open" .
<http://www.example.org/medicalOntology#FSCA-001> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "CorrectiveAction 001 - Safety alert for HeartMate thrombosis risk" .
